cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with labeled sequence transduction, which is a task related to natural language processing. The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The mention of latent variables indicates that it could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the mention of a benchmark suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), although this is less likely than the other categories mentioned.
